page.title: 03Laykin Art.
page.content: "Sithi dad ar tha gooin aht toneet?" "no" "alreit al gooin call fo mi mate" "a tha laykin art" "why wis tha gooin" "darn tu chipoil fo some fish n chips" I et mi fish but chip's wu gammy so a wanged um. Then wi went darn tu tennis cooarts fora game ur tennis.Abart 10 minutes later some hard guys kem un sed "gerof ueea wi wonar game" So wi went an ed ur game ur golf. A sloged ball un it went straait thru wonar comps winduz un set burglar alarm off un wi run like ELL. Wi went darn om but the wu nobdy in so wi went darn t'shop un bowt some spice. When wi got om bobies wu art side mi ooam un wi said, "MY GOD BOBBIES UR ERE"so wi went in un wi erd "gerrup er" so wi went up un mi mam sed "al tanyur backside foyur." Wen wi got up theer shi sent us ter bed.
